LVMH Starts Sparkling-Wine JV in Northwest China, Xinhua Says

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-05-24T15:56:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-24/lvmh-starts-sparkling-wine-jv-in-northwest-china-xinhua-says.html
LVMH Moet Hennessy Louis Vuitton SA
started a project to make sparkling wine in northwestern  China â€™s
Ningxia province, Xinhua News Agency reported, citing the
regional reclamation bureau.  LVMH and Ningxia Reclamation Group will establish a winery
with 1,000 mu (67 hectares) of grapes at the eastern foot of
Helan Mountain, Xinhua said today, citing Chang Limin, deputy
director of the reclamation bureau and deputy general manager of
the reclamation group.  The reclamation group will separately grow a further 1,700
mu of grapes for the winery, the official news service said.  To contact the Bloomberg News staff for this story:
